So I thought this PR was to address the issue of updating one field of a nested pr, e.g. say the default was:

```
{
   foo: {
      bar: 3
      baz: 4
    }
}
```

I should be able to override with `{foo: {bar: 100}}`. That doesn't require setting allow unknown to false right?

if using unique_ptr, then the code will look like,

